text:
Have been eating Vietnamese pho, bang mi, spring rolls . The  curry chicken goes well with their Vietnamese baguette,
The lady boss told me to try the porridge. So tapow the curry chicken & added 3 baguettes and a pork century egg porridge
I reheat the porridge hot, added an egg n added fried shallots.
It was indeed a nice delicious porridge 👍😋😀

Excellent food paired with friendly service at this stall which offers a combination of Vietnamese and Chinese cuisine.

The ban mian broth is hearty while the noodles are al dente, and the Vietnamese grilled pork noodles come with a generous helping of tender pork, vegetables and herbs for a refreshing meal.
Kinda rude but the food is decent and they use Vietnamese pepper.
